<paragraph id="5108975156C475D583D4C68200FB8D52" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">
<taxonomicName id="B657B70E374AD7C05902CDB5CADB7FA0" authority="Gay" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Aethionema" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="null" pageNumber="140" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="thomasianum">
<normalizedToken id="4A1C8504231F4469E2A8F73598DF3B97" originalValue="Aëthionema" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Aethionema</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="593E47010B586DF45E3B8296B9C13CAE" originalValue="Thomasiánum" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Thomasianum</normalizedToken>
Gay
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="50DF56D0A9DB9D98935338A9603A5B4E" pageId="null" pageNumber="140" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="7F0079CEA4C93135EA8659AD4FCB6C5A" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Thomas-Steinkresse</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="6A63804F4E058DACBBC84225E7449FFD" pageId="null" pageNumber="140" type="description">
<paragraph id="9A118E1DE658B0F3896AD7A42E0D47B2" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="8843AF5600DE3B1CB400F512529EDBFA" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Iberis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="null" pageNumber="140" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="saxatilis">
<emphasis id="8781A757C0C9B9ACB2A5BC17B9B51233" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">A. saxatilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<normalizedToken id="942A399A30A43D110289E7C9572A9378" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
oval, 2-4mal so lang wie breit; 
<emphasis id="67DB869BDF9AC410CFAFFACB8A736D93" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">
Fruchtstand dicht, 
<normalizedToken id="A74779384675D56BD0426970223DA751" originalValue="eiförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">eifoermig</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="AE7CAB1A3353B42BEAF6AE8B7BAE79D4" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
6-9 mm lang und 
<emphasis id="52BD991EA046F746084F900FEB2290A0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">
8-12 mm breit, mit 2,5-5 mm breitem Rand, der 2-5mal so breit ist wie die 
<normalizedToken id="EC537AD0E664F18DDDC8B6A1BD945A97" originalValue="Hälfte" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Haelfte</normalizedToken>
der restlichen Frucht
</emphasis>
, 1-2samig, als Ganzes abfallend; Griffel an der Frucht 0,3-0,5 mm lang; 
<emphasis id="1E07925D33ED4310993A21BA2AEFE60F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Samen 1,7-2 mm lang</emphasis>
, 
<normalizedToken id="1B2654A7899A217D11F2EFFE82FBFAB5" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">+/-</normalizedToken>
glatt.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A0485B55483B61128C5669E9B7B023F8" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">
<emphasis id="6E36ACFE85270C2A2C183AFA2911271D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="D99A89D8F134638AE8464BEE3FE5F041" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">24:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="ED6D958E1B3B75E433BABEC4F5EA59EF" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
Gran Paradiso und Lautaret (Favarger und Huynh in 
<normalizedToken id="B145E9183C4F194593C12391E35952FE" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Loeve</normalizedToken>
und Solbrig 1964a, Favarger 1965). 
<emphasis id="5FEE51BA8938F5580DF21B69CADBCEE9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="BDF7C49039D479BAAD8C44D2E6439CD9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">36:</emphasis>
Material aus botan ischem Garten (Manton 1932).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4B24D84014720FCC5FE37B8F67AABA09" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">
<emphasis id="BCE4E8C2504793AE0E9F2BC9BBC6F43D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin und alpin (1800-2500 m). Lockerer, feiner, kalkreicher Schieferschutt.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0B3F634C0F8B24682DDFB6C31B96B97B" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">
<emphasis id="5CE29ADF86EBA759EB87ADB4E4BDC241" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Verbreitung. Grajische Pflanze:</emphasis>
Um Cogne im Aostatal, nur an wenigen Stellen. 
<normalizedToken id="4A2B6FF42559EF79CC3FF578012ADBCE" originalValue="Außerhalb" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Ausserhalb</normalizedToken>
des Gebiets nur noch zwischen Col 
<normalizedToken id="42750853B459550DC9F6BC1E5FDD785F" originalValue="d’Izoard" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">d'Izoard</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="59F2CE11766BAEC0F6ED87A121EFD360" originalValue="Briançon" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Briancon</normalizedToken>
(Braun-Blanquet 1922).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="69D3EF33BE2709663F8D8B31A82E67E8" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">
<emphasis id="379CA185561C2FBF24A7DEF71EEB301E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">
Bemerkungen. 
<taxonomicName id="4BD5809356A80FFE2ED12C2A7ED5A441" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Aethionema" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="null" pageNumber="140" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="thomasianum">A. Thomasianum</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
soll angeblich auch in Kabylien (Algerien) wachsen (vgl. auch Becherer 1945). Die Beschreibung bei Quezel und Santa (1962) stimmt aber nicht mit unserer Pflanze 
<normalizedToken id="3B7B75DDB438510C6AF4DDDE3AF6B87F" originalValue="überein" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">ueberein</normalizedToken>
(Frucht 4-8-samig; Griffel 
<normalizedToken id="6AE4BDB5E5BCF59D775CECF2FD3328DC" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">laenger</normalizedToken>
als der 
<normalizedToken id="BBF2C5598039BFAD87C8EBEEE3E23AC1" originalValue="Flügel" pageId="null" pageNumber="140">Fluegel</normalizedToken>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
